msgid "The front door."
msgstr "前门。"

msgid "I need to paint a red symbol here..."
msgstr "我需要在这里画一个红色的符号..."

msgid "The front door. There's still no red symbol painted on it."
msgstr "前门。我还未在此处画上红色符号。"

msgid "Go inside?"
msgstr "要进去吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_Exterior_Front.event_paint_needed.choice.Go inside?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_Exterior_Front.event_paint_needed.choice.Go inside?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "(You filled up the bird food bowl inside.)"
msgstr "（你把里面的鸟食碗装满了。）"

msgid "I don't know if I can feed it directly... Let's fill the bird feeder instead."
msgstr "我不知道我能不能直接喂它...还是把饲鸟器装满吧。"

msgid "The bird food goes in the bird house."
msgstr "鸟食正放在鸟舍里。"

msgid "Let's try it..."
msgstr "让我们来试试看吧..."

msgid "Oh... oh no... lipstick on wood doesn't work at all."
msgstr "哦...哦不...口红在木头上完全写不出来。"

msgid "This thing is also completely ruined."
msgstr "这玩意完全不能用了。"

msgid "I hope mother won't get angry..."
msgstr "我希望妈妈不要生气..."

msgid "...Nah. I'll get rid of it and pretend it never existed."
msgstr "...哎。把它扔掉，然后当它从来就不存在吧。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_Exterior_Front.item_lipstick_on_door.dlg.narrator"
msgid "It's already done."
msgstr "已经完成了。"

msgid "Time to draw..."
msgstr "画画时间到..."

msgid "What a strange symbol..."
msgstr "真是个奇怪的符号啊..."

msgid "Now the house will be even more cursed than it already was."
msgstr "现在，这所房子将受到比原来更严重的诅咒。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_Exterior_Front.item_paint_on_door.dlg.narrator"
msgid "It's already done."
msgstr "已经完成了。"

msgid "I already salted the other door, that should be good enough."
msgstr "我已经在别的门上撒过了盐，这应该已经足够了。"

msgid "The salt probably goes on the inner door, not here."
msgstr "盐应该在门内撒，而不是这里。"

msgid "That wouldn't be good for the birds."
msgstr "这对鸟儿可不好。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_Exterior_Front.item_salt_on_door.dlg.lacie"
msgid "The salt goes on the inside only..."
msgstr "只用在室内撒盐..."

msgid "Also, I'll clean up the drawing tomorrow, since it's not in the instructions."
msgstr "另外，我明天还要清理这个涂鸦，虽然这个没写在教程上。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_Exterior_Front.item_salt_on_garage_door.dlg.lacie"
msgid "The salt goes on the inside only..."
msgstr "只用在室内撒盐..."

msgid "The gates probably don't need salt."
msgstr "大门口应该不需要撒盐。"

msgid "A birdhouse."
msgstr "鸟居。"

msgid "We don't get many birds, but I leave food here for them in case."
msgstr "我们家的鸟不多，但我还是给它们留了食物，以防万一。"

msgid "Where did I put that bag..?"
msgstr "我把袋子放哪儿了..？"

msgid "Various red and blue flowers."
msgstr "各种红色与蓝色的花朵。"

msgid "Bright blue flowers."
msgstr "亮蓝色的花朵。"

msgid "These lamps turn on automatically at night."
msgstr "这些灯在晚上会自动开启。"

msgid "These lamps turn off automatically during the day."
msgstr "这些灯在白天会自动关闭。"

msgid "The curtains prevent you from looking in."
msgstr "窗帘让你无法看到内部。"

msgid "The garage door. It requires a remote control to open from the outside."
msgstr "车库门。需要遥控器才能从外面打开。"

msgid "A sturdy black gate meant for cars."
msgstr "一扇坚固的黑色大门，专供汽车通行。"

msgid "A small lamppost."
msgstr "一个小灯柱。"

msgid "The neighbor's front yard is on the other side."
msgstr "邻居家的前院就在另一侧。"

msgid "I shouldn't stare... and give them another reason to dislike me."
msgstr "我不应该看过去的...然后给他们另一个不喜欢我的理由。"

msgid "A crow keeps watch in front of your house."
msgstr "一只乌鸦在你家门口守望着。"

msgid "Maybe it's waiting for some food?"
msgstr "也许它在等着吃东西呢？"

msgid "I brought the bird food with me, I just have to fill up the feeder."
msgstr "我带了鸟食，只需要把喂食器装满就可以了。"

msgid "The feeder is full, but it doesn't seem to care..."
msgstr "喂食器已经满了，但它似乎并不在乎..."

msgid "A large tree."
msgstr "一棵大树。"

msgid "Its leaves look nice in fall."
msgstr "它的叶子在秋天很好看。"

msgid "A small tree."
msgstr "一棵小树。"

msgid "I'd rather go inside right now."
msgstr "我宁可现在去室内。"

msgid "The front gate."
msgstr "大门。"

msgid "I don't want to go back outside..."
msgstr "我不想回到外面去了..."

msgid "Get on the bus?"
msgstr "要登上巴士吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_Exterior_Front.move_exit.choice.Get on the bus?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_Exterior_Front.move_exit.choice.Get on the bus?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "The bus isn't here yet."
msgstr "巴士现在还没来。"

msgid "The bus isn't here so... Let's just clean up."
msgstr "巴士没有来，所以...让我们开始清理工作吧。"

msgid "Where to?"
msgstr "要去哪里？"
